A '''patrol special''' triggers its special whenever a {{Class|PatrolPoint|patrol point}} with the same {{c|[[TID|tid]]}} is used by a monster on patrol.
==== [[DECORATE]] definition ====
 ACTOR <u>PatrolSpecial</u>
 {
   {{Property|Radius}} 8
   {{Property|Height}} 8
   {{Property|Mass}} 10
   +{{Flag|NOGRAVITY}}
   +{{Flag|NOBLOCKMAP}}
   +{{Flag|DONTSPLASH}}
   {{Property|RenderStyle}} None
 }
